@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_aiotba(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin((wp.abs(v0 + 0.81) + (v2 + 0.06 + v2 + 0.19)))
    v0 = (0.16 - v2)
    v2 = wp.cos(0.47)
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.95) - tmp) / (0.21 / v1))
    v1 = (wp.abs(0.70) / v0)
    v2 = (0.46 / (0.31 + wp.abs(tmp + 0.25)))
    tmp = wp.sin(v2)
    data[tid] = v0
